      "name": "fresh parsley",
      "amount": "2 tbsp, chopped",
      "notes": "optional garnish"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and cook for one minute.",
    "Pour in beef broth and bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add smoked paprika, salt, and pepper, and stir well.",
    "Reduce heat and add cubed fromage-blanc, letting it soften for five minutes.",
    "Fold in chopped fermented kimchi and goat milk, cooking until the stew is velvety.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley if desired."
  ],
